Group 6: Platform Management
20. system_config
A key-value store for platform-wide numeric configuration parameters. Allows admins to tune business rules without code changes — for example, adjusting the deposit percentage or platform fee rate.

Field Name	Data Type	Key / Constraint	Field Function & Description
